tion" target="L00142">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 10. 12. 1892</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L00144">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 23. 12. [1892]</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00142">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 10. 12. 1892</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00145">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 25. 12. 1892</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
